板是和云平台通讯的主要模块<br>主要负责上传桩电压、电流电量等各种数据<br>和执行云平台下发的充电、断电、过压保护等命令<br>是整个互联网+流程的终端设备</div><div class="app1link app1link2"><a href='tencent://message/?uin=568615539&amp;Site=QQ/&amp;Menu=yes' target="qqtraget" title="硬件咨询">硬件咨询</a><a href='tencent://message/?uin=469100943&amp;Site=QQ/&amp;Menu=yes' target="qqtraget" title="软件咨询">软件咨询</a></div></div></div><div class="net4bot webmask1"><a name="3"></a></div></div><div class="net4out"><div class="net2 widths"><img src="/Web/Home/Public/images/net/net4.png" class="netimg2" title="充电桩云平台" alt="充电桩云平台" /><div class="net2left net4left"><h3 class="net2tit" style="color:#fff">网络充电桩云平台</h3><div class="net2txt" style="color:#fff">云平台是互联网+流程的中枢<br>负责为用户提供服务，接收和中转数据，下发指令，充电计费等功能<br>其作用不可取代</div><div class="app1link" style="padding-left:100px"><a href='tencent://message/?uin=568615539&amp;Site=QQ/&amp;Menu=yes' target="qqtraget" title="硬件咨询">硬件咨询</a><a href='tencent://message/?uin=469100943&amp;Site=QQ/&amp;Menu=yes' target="qqtraget" title="软件咨询">软件咨询</a></div></div></div><div class="net5bot webmask2"><a name="4"></a></div></div><div class="net3 widths" style="height:400px"><img src="/Web/Home/Public/images/net/net5.png" class="netimg3" title="用户充电APP" alt="用户充电APP" /><div class="net3right" style="width:640px"><h3 class="net3tit" style="color:#888; padding-top:80px">用户充电APP</h3><div class="net3txt" style="color:#888">运行于用户的手机端，是移动设备上的客户端<br>为用户提供站点导航、在线充值、扫码充电等信息</div><div class="app1link app1link1"><a href='tencent://message/?uin=568615539&amp;Site=QQ/&amp;Menu=yes' target="qqtraget" title="硬件咨询">硬件咨询</a><a href='tencent://message/?uin=469100943&amp;Site=QQ/&amp;Menu=yes' target="qqtraget" title="软件咨询">软件咨询</a></div></div></div><script>$(function(){setwidth();$(window).resize(function(){setwidth()})});function setwidth(){$(".webmask").css({"border-left":"#d6203f solid "+$(document).width()+"px"});$(".webmask1").css({"border-right":"#29548b solid "+$(document).width()+"px"});$(".webmask2").css({"border-left":"#fff solid "+$(document)